courier-authlib: courier-authlib (A generic authentication API)
courier-authlib:
courier-authlib: The Courier Authentication Library is a generic authentication API
courier-authlib: that encapsulates the process of validating account passwords. In
courier-authlib: addition to reading the traditional account passwords from
courier-authlib: /etc/passwd, the account information can alternatively be obtained
courier-authlib: from an LDAP directory; a MySQL or a PostgreSQL database; or a
courier-authlib: GDBM or a DB file.
courier-authlib: http://www.courier-mta.org/imap/
courier-authlib:
courier-authlib: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
